<p>Welcome to Go Newsletter Issue #28. A couple of interesting events have happened since the last issue: Gocon in Japan, and the first Docker conference. You'll find links to talks and code from these events below. Also, Go 1.3rc1 has been released, and rc2 is not far away.</p>
<p>Compiled by <a href="https://twitter.com/mattrco">Matt Cottingham</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/kelseyhightower">Kelsey Hightower</a>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
